{"tid":1044112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理工大學校董劉銘章暗示關sir係因其港獨主張被踢出校","createTime":"2019-03-02T16:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T03:26:47.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc2e8fd4392f93ef398d7b3d0102f7e9f1a0511","tid":1044112,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"理大校董劉炳章表示，辱罵事件在去年發生後，他已不斷在校董會要求校方跟進，其他學校迅速處理，但理大卻花了約幾個月才能作出判決，形容這是遲來的判決。他強調，今次紀委會的決定是適當，外國也有類似的情況，若然涉及種族歧視，根本是要勒令有關學生退學。&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;嚴重損害國家尊嚴，理大是受到公家資助，大家有責任維護聲譽，維護國家尊嚴。他又說，理大應該制定相關指引，若然教職員日後面對類似的情況，可以如何處理，希望教職員日後不要示弱。"},{"pid":"d48cf271a0094e5beeda955f1441ecca50cf392b","tid":1044112,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"劉炳章至啱，sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e87423a3c2bdedeec32726de90331a80b290c1d","tid":1044112,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T23:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4484b98c6500ef6acd3cfbee67913812fe6731","tid":1044112,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}